{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be innovative and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Red Audio Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e63946;\n            --secondary-color: #f1faee;\n            --text-color: #1d3557;\n            --dark-text-color: #000000;\n            --hover-color: #d62839;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        section h2::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 50%;\n            bottom: -8px;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 4px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            border-radius: 2px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-content {\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-content p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: #555;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .listen-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .listen-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--hover-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 4rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero-animation {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--hover-color) 100%);\n            opacity: 0.3;\n            animation: pulse 4s infinite ease-in-out;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.5; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }\n        }\n\n        .animated-text {\n            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out forwards;\n            opacity: 0;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card .animated-text {\n            animation-delay: calc(var(--i) * 0.2s);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"hero-animation\"></div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1 class=\"animated-text\">Red Audio Network</h1>\n            <p class=\"animated-text\">Your Hub for Captivating Stories and Insightful Conversations</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2 class=\"animated-text\">What We Do</h2>\n                <p class=\"animated-text\">At Red Audio Network, we're passionate about bringing you the most engaging podcasts across a diverse range of genres. From true crime to technology, comedy to culture, we curate and produce content that sparks curiosity and conversation.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"podcasts\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2 class=\"animated-text\">Featured Podcasts</h2>\n                <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-card\" style=\"--i: 0;\">\n                        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e63946/ffffff?text=Podcast+1\" alt=\"Podcast 1 Cover\">\n                        <div class=\"podcast-content\">\n                            <h3 class=\"animated-text\">The Crimson Chronicle</h3>\n                            <p class=\"animated-text\">Dive deep into untold stories and uncover the mysteries that lie beneath the surface. A gripping true-crime experience.</p>\n                            <button class=\"listen-button animated-text\">Listen Now</button>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"podcast-card\" style=\"--i: 1;\">\n                        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/d62839/ffffff?text=Podcast+2\" alt=\"Podcast 2 Cover\">\n                        <div class=\"podcast-content\">\n                            <h3 class=\"animated-text\">Red Shift</h3>\n                            <p class=\"animated-text\">Explore the future of technology, innovation, and the digital world. Hosted by leading industry experts.</p>\n                            <button class=\"listen-button animated-text\">Listen Now</button>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"podcast-card\" style=\"--i: 2;\">\n                        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/e63946/ffffff?text=Podcast+3\" alt=\"Podcast 3 Cover\">\n                        <div class=\"podcast-content\">\n                            <h3 class=\"animated-text\">The Ruby Rant</h3>\n                            <p class=\"animated-text\">Unfiltered opinions and hilarious takes on pop culture, current events, and everything in between. Get ready to laugh!</p>\n                            <button class=\"listen-button animated-text\">Listen Now</button>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Red Audio Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const animatedElements = document.querySelectorAll('.animated-text');\n            animatedElements.forEach((el, index) => {\n                el.style.animationDelay = `${index * 0.1}s`;\n                el.style.opacity = 1;\n                el.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';\n            });\n\n            const podcastCards = document.querySelectorAll('.podcast-card');\n            podcastCards.forEach((card, index) => {\n                card.style.setProperty('--i', index);\n                const contentElements = card.querySelectorAll('.animated-text');\n                contentElements.forEach((el, i) => {\n                    el.style.animationDelay = `${index * 0.3 + i * 0.15}s`;\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}